      Per architecture Â§6.4 (promote-to-matter flow â€” Accept + Reject paths emit `memory.promotion_resolved`; Accept additionally emits `memory.fact_promoted`; both emit `context.decision_made` for T6), ADR-030 v2 (memory channel), spec FR-32 (canonical payloads). T6 audit (`context.decision_made`) is tier-1-safe (no fact text) per ADR-015.
    </background>
