  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load architecture Â§6.4 (Approve + Reject branches) + ADR-030 v2 + ADR-015 (T6 audit shape).</step>
    <step order="2">Read `MatterMemoryPromotionService.cs` â€” locate Approve + Reject success paths.</step>
    <step order="3">In `ApproveAsync` success path, AFTER `IMatterMemoryService.AppendFactAsync` returns success:
      - Emit `memory.fact_promoted { factId, matterId, source }` on `memory` channel.
