      - Emit `context.decision_made { decision: "promotion_rejected", promotionId, matterId }` on `context` channel (T6 audit).
    </step>
    <step order="5">Extend unit tests at `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Memory/MatterMemoryPromotionServiceTests.cs`:
